<bibRefCitation id="77BF797470E58CA608CE745FF0AE88AA" author="Della Giustina, William" journalOrPublisher="Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7716435" refString="Della Giustina, William, 2019. Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1&amp;2. Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" title="Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1 &amp; 2" year="2019">Della Giustina (2019)</bibRefCitation>
does not support the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName id="B2E832B8873FCC9628B20BC9C6EF3AA6" genus="E." lsidName="E. basilinea" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" rank="species" species="basilinea">
<emphasis id="2BA9E575EB285EBB36FAAF0C179ECABC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">E. basilinea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Germar, 1821) under 
<taxonomicName id="31A618F7E0C3F9CC9B210D23ED9CAE24" genus="E." lsidName="E. speciosa" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis id="1A3F59EE4DA10B97CA6C78C18E40B56C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">E. speciosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
proposed by 
<bibRefCitation id="B15113F23A5203BE8EBADFB553A461B1" author="Nast, J." journalOrPublisher="Annales Zoologici" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="297 - 307" refId="B7727628" refString="Nast, J., 1986. Notes on some Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) VI - X. Annales Zoologici 40 (2-5): 297 - 307" title="Notes on some Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) VI - X" volume="40" year="1986">Nast (1986)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="62EEF06A025986CF98F16D840907B135" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="C76D1DDB5EAB805B93A296DA8F6C5C54" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="78ACC9B33A57477B1D757AFE1827758D" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
Norway, Denmark, Sweden, Finland, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Russia (Karelia) (
<bibRefCitation id="21711C92A7FD7FBA862E6D07203EE846" author="Soederman, Guy" journalOrPublisher="Cicadina" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="33 - 69" refId="B7712829" refString="Soederman, Guy, Gillerfors, Gosta, Endrestol, Anders, Soederman, Guy, 2009. An annotated catalogue of the Auchenorrhyncha of Northern Europe. Cicadina 10 (1): 33 - 69" title="An annotated catalogue of the Auchenorrhyncha of Northern Europe" volume="10" year="2009">
<normalizedToken id="FFB17B86ED5F7AC728853C6FC4FD7C65" originalValue="Söderman">Soederman</normalizedToken>
et al. 2009
</bibRefCitation>
), Germany, Austria, Switzerland (
<bibRefCitation id="87133117E25B1798CA4E5881738BF28F" author="Muehlethaler, Roland" journalOrPublisher="Wiebelsheim" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7834856" refString="Muehlethaler, Roland, Holzinger, Werner E, Nickel, Herbert, Wachmann, Ekkehard, 2018. Die Zikaden Deutschlands, Oesterreichs und der Schweiz: Entdecken - Beobachten - Bestimmen. Wiebelsheim" title="Die Zikaden Deutschlands, Oesterreichs und der Schweiz: Entdecken - Beobachten - Bestimmen" year="2018">
<normalizedToken id="8BCAF1A7E2DB1B130AF75F63EE7CB228" originalValue="Mühlethaler">Muehlethaler</normalizedToken>
et al. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
), Luxembourg (
<bibRefCitation id="33CF3711D9E664AA2DB6FAAA5FBAA2BE" author="Niedringhaus, Rolf" journalOrPublisher="Ferrantia" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="1 - 105" refId="B7712748" refString="Niedringhaus, Rolf, Biedermann, Robert, Nickel, Herbert, 2010. Verbreitungsatlas der Zikaden des Grossherzogtums Luxemburg - Textband. Ferrantia 60: 1 - 105" title="Verbreitungsatlas der Zikaden des Grossherzogtums Luxemburg - Textband" volume="60" year="2010">Niedringhaus et al. 2010a</bibRefCitation>
), as 
<taxonomicName id="13B47A52B68FAD0ACDA3F4BFA7F57C5F" genus="E." lsidName="E. basilinea" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" rank="species" species="basilinea">
<emphasis id="2EC1C588C5D6D22D77E567D42C4A179A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">E. basilinea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Germar, 1821). Synonimisation is refuted by 
<bibRefCitation id="B05560E0B822A99A224B00AEF7F8E8DD" author="Della Giustina, William" journalOrPublisher="Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7716435" refString="Della Giustina, William, 2019. Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1&amp;2. Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" title="Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1 &amp; 2" year="2019">Della Giustina (2019)</bibRefCitation>
for the North of Europe. France (
<bibRefCitation id="A530E01C982DE35A959C01D5C9D2730C" author="Della Giustina, William" journalOrPublisher="Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7716435" refString="Della Giustina, William, 2019. Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1&amp;2. Federation Francaise des Societes de Sciences Naturelles" title="Les Delphacidae de France et des pays limitrophes (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha) Tome 1 &amp; 2" year="2019">Della Giustina 2019</bibRefCitation>
), Hungary (
<bibRefCitation id="559E1CD853632FE79006CC91308F037C" author="Asche, Manfred" journalOrPublisher="Marburger Entomologische Publikationen" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="139 - 154" refId="B7712545" refString="Asche, Manfred, 1982. Beitraege zur Delphaciden-Fauna Ungarns (Homoptera Cicadina Delphacidae). Marburger Entomologische Publikationen 1 (7): 139 - 154" title="Beitraege zur Delphaciden-Fauna Ungarns (Homoptera Cicadina Delphacidae)" volume="1" year="1982">Asche 1982a</bibRefCitation>
), ex-Yugoslavia (
<bibRefCitation id="9A56C4F098ED1474B2EEA39F86C33546" author="Asche, Manfred" journalOrPublisher="Marburger Entomologische Publikationen" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="99 - 138" refId="B7712757" refString="Asche, Manfred, 1982. Beitraege zur Delphaciden - Fauna Jugoslawiens und Bulgariens (Homoptera Cicadina Delphacidae). Marburger Entomologische Publikationen 1 (7): 99 - 138" title="Beitraege zur Delphaciden - Fauna Jugoslawiens und Bulgariens (Homoptera Cicadina Delphacidae)" volume="1" year="1982">Asche 1982b</bibRefCitation>
), Belarus (
<bibRefCitation id="BD7893C97F381122F3759055113C155F" author="Borodin, Oleg" journalOrPublisher="Beitraege zur Zikadenkunde" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="29 - 47" refId="B7712793" refString="Borodin, Oleg, 2004. A checklist of the Auchenorrhyncha of Belarus (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha et Cicadomorpha). Beitraege zur Zikadenkunde 7: 29 - 47" title="A checklist of the Auchenorrhyncha of Belarus (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha et Cicadomorpha)" volume="7" year="2004">Borodin 2004</bibRefCitation>
), Kazakhstan (
<bibRefCitation id="A776BD2FC738A2C9B061B34CDCABA39A" author="Mitjaev, I D" journalOrPublisher="Science of Kazakh SSR" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="1 - 211" refId="B7716602" refString="Mitjaev, I D, 1971. Leafhoppers of Kazakhstan (Homoptera - Cicadinea). Science of Kazakh SSR 1971: 1 - 211" title="Leafhoppers of Kazakhstan (Homoptera - Cicadinea)" volume="1971" year="1971">Mitjaev 1971</bibRefCitation>
), Korea (
<bibRefCitation id="A43219351B54D66B9872E2A8B6C136E3" author="Park, Jaekook" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Asia-Pacific Biodiversity" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="310 - 313" refId="B7712437" refString="Park, Jaekook, Jung, Sunghoon, 2020. Two newly recorded genera and species of the plant hopper (Hemiptera: Auchenorhyncha: Delphacidae) in Korea. Journal of Asia-Pacific Biodiversity 13 (2): 310 - 313" title="Two newly recorded genera and species of the plant hopper (Hemiptera: Auchenorhyncha: Delphacidae) in Korea" volume="13" year="2020">Park and Jung 2020</bibRefCitation>
), Japan (
<bibRefCitation id="5EF9C256A8431000F165E84CFB92BC56" author="Hayashi, M." journalOrPublisher="Entomological Society of Japan" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7716526" refString="Hayashi, M., Fujinuma, Satoshi, 2016. Catalogue of the Insects of Japan Volume 4 Paraneoptera (Psocodea, Thysanoptera, Hemiptera). Entomological Society of Japan" title="Catalogue of the Insects of Japan Volume 4 Paraneoptera (Psocodea, Thysanoptera, Hemiptera)" year="2016">Hayashi and Fujinuma 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="11580B452D639431C14DEA9063755B13" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" type="notes">
<paragraph id="A6092E15095FDB2D35138A4098C9A0F4" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BE75DABFD71BB0B76040090B2047FE81" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">
New record for Bulgaria. 
<emphasis id="1E7BD721E647AC091B655B9909CB02C8" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Western Danube Plain</emphasis>
: Archar vill., 04.v.2015, 1♂; 
<emphasis id="FF7936FD3A08983F57B962F1F2BF79FF" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231">Southern Black Sea coast</emphasis>
: Atia vill., 22.viii.2016, 1♂. Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="30DB4E93BFA2FC50B7CEA8F81E954C08" author="Gjonov, I." journalOrPublisher="Annals of the Upper Silesian Museum in Bytom. Entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" refId="B7727581" refString="Gjonov, I., 2022. new_fulgoromorpha_records_bulgaria_2022. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="new _ fulgoromorpha _ records _ bulgaria _ 2022" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Gjonov (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
